parameters.adj_close: The close price adjusted for both dividends and splits.
parameters.date: The date expressed as Date values.
parameters.volume: The number of trades for the given date.
parameters.open, high, low, close:
The day's opening, high, low, and closing
prices in USD. The close price is adjusted for splits.

description:
Description
This dataset provides daily price indicators for the S&P 500 index from the
beginning of 1950 to the end of 2015. The index includes 500 leading
companies and captures about 80 percent coverage of available market
capitalization.
title: Daily S&P 500 Index data from 1950 to 2015
reference: Here is a glimpse at the data available in sp500.
